  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales Coordinator (1-Year Contract)",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for a <strong>Sales Coordinator</strong> to support the promotion and administration of our security training programmes. This role is ideal for someone who enjoys customer interaction, is organised, and has an interest in the training and security industry.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Promote and sell security training courses</p></li><li><p>Assist trainees with course registration and enrolment</p></li><li><p>Respond to trainee enquiries on training courses and general security industry matters</p></li><li><p>Handle sales enquiries via phone calls and emails</p></li><li><p>Develop, maintain, and update client and trainee databases</p></li><li><p>Perform other duties as assigned by management</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Minimum GCE “O” Level qualification</p></li><li><p>Proficient in Microsoft Office (Word, Excel, Outlook)</p></li><li><p>Good command of spoken and written English</p></li><li><p>Preferably at least 1 year of experience in selling training courses or related services</p></li><li><p>Good interpersonal and communication skills</p></li></ul><p><strong>Why Join Us</strong></p><ul><li><p>Exposure to the security training and education sector</p></li><li><p>Hands-on experience in sales coordination and customer engagement</p></li><li><p>Supportive working environment with opportunities to learn and grow</p></li></ul><p>Interested candidates are welcome to submit their applications with a detailed resume.</p>",
